ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Designating the President of the Queen's Privy Council for Canada as the responsible minister for the purposes of the Act
PrecisOrder (a) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2006-81 of February 6, 2006; and (b) designating the PRESIDENT OF THE QUEEN'S PRIVY COUNCIL FOR CANADA, a member of the Queen’s Privy Council for Canada, as the responsible MINISTER for the purposes of the REFERENDUM ACT, effective November 4, 2015.
